room_title: Escape room "Meltdown" by OB-Xscape Rooms in Southern Shores
room_address: 1 Ocean Boulevard  Suite 109 Southern Shores, NC 27949
room_description: Your mission is to enter the evil professor's secret laboratory. He is initiating a meltdown of his ESCAPE reactor that will cause excessive damage to all mankind if the final stage of the launch is completed. You must search the lab and find a way to stop the reactor in time to save our planet!
